        <item>
            <title>神改便携式 Mac Mini   桌面机化身随身工作站</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/portable-mac-mini/3d-%e6%89%93%e5%8d%b0/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=portable-mac-mini</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/28/portable-mac-mini/3d-%e6%89%93%e5%8d%b0/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 28 Apr 2025 08:50:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[3D 打印]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305258</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在行动办公成为新常态的今天，桌面电脑是否还只能困守一隅？近日有一位 YouTuber 自己动手，成功将 Apple 最新 M4 Mac Mini 创造成一款可携式装置，结合键盘、触控萤幕及创新的 3D 列印结构，不但大幅提升机动性，还保留了原有性能与扩充性，为爱好 DIY 与行动工作者带来全新启发。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini87screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>重新定义 Mac Mini 使用方式</h2><p>影片创作者表示，收到不少观众留言，期待看到新的 Mac Mini 改装作品。当他实际上手 Mac Mini，发现其极致小巧的机身后，便萌生了「让桌机随身携带」的想法。有别于以往需要额外携带键盘的设计，这次他选择将 Apple 的 Magic Keyboard 直接融入结构中，再搭配一块支援 VESA 标准的触控萤幕，大小几乎与键盘一致。这块萤幕只需一条连接线即可驱动，兼具便携与功能性，成为可携式 Mac Mini 的关键组件。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini625screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini15screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>巧妙设计，解决平衡与收纳问题</h2><p>由于萤幕重量明显大于键盘，为防止翻倒，创作者灵机一动，利用 Mac Mini 本体为键盘侧边增重，巧妙解决结构平衡问题。同时为避免遮挡插槽与电源键，他将 Mac Mini 横向置于萤幕下方，既维持美观，也符合人体工学。所有核心零件，包括萤幕连接线、散热孔、风扇进气口及各式插槽，都在设计中被完整保留，不影响日常使用。而 Mac Mini 本体则透过魔术胶带固定，方便拆卸与维护。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini117screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/m4macini136screensho.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
